o\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"enough market share\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cognitive bias also seems to have influencedTheranosinvestors' decisions.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cognitive bias\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"influencedTheranosinvestors' decisions\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, how can business leaders avoid these cognitive blunders?\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"business leaders\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"these cognitive blunders\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Luckily, psychology offers insights and actions to help.\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"psychology\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"insights\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"actions\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly articulate what constitutes success before making critical decisions.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"critical decisions\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What knowledge, skills, and other characteristics do you need on the team to deliver your vision, and does the candidate possess them, or do you just like them more than other candidates?\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What knowledge\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"skills\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"other characteristics\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"your vision\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"the candidate\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"other candidates\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How will you measure the success of your product or service; will it be market share, profit margin, customer satisfaction, employee experience, or something else?\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"your product\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"service\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"market share\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"profit margin\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"customer satisfaction\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"employee experience\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Make sure everyone involved in the decision understands the key factors that should influence their decisions.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2664}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"the key factors\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"their decisions\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Develop a team culture that prizes critical analysis over urgent reactions.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team culture\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"critical analysis\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"urgent reactions\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not over-rely on the most familiar information.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most familiar information\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Challenge employees by asking, \\\"What might we be missing here?\\\"\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Challenge\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"employees\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Create a respectful culture where employees feel seen, heard, and valued and can express their opinions without fear of retribution.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a respectful culture\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"employees\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"their opinions\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3052}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3065}, {\"ngram\": \"retribution\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do the decision-making norms in your organizations support effective outcomes?\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision-making norms\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"your organizations\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"effective outcomes\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do the employees closest to the decision-impact get the chance to express their lessons of experience?\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the employees\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision-impact\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"their lessons\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do leaders over-rely on consultants versus employees when making critical decisions?\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"consultants\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"employees\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"critical decisions\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do managers take ownership of decisions or say, \\\"This came from the top of the house.\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"managers\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"ownership\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3421}, {\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I disagree, but we have to do it?\\\"\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic officials do not rely on one person or one high-speed camera to make their final judgments; neither should you.\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic officials\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3489}, {\"ngram\": \"one person\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"one high-speed camera\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3540}, {\"ngram\": \"their final judgments\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes, the most discerning perspective can come from the fresh eyes of someone outside your inner circle.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most discerning perspective\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3634}, {\"ngram\": \"the fresh eyes\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3663}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"your inner circle\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And do not hesitate to bring in outside experts to analyze complex situations from multiple angles.\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"outside experts\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"complex situations\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple angles\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Research indicates that experts generally make better decisions than novices.\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Research\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3810}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 3826, \"to\": 3833}, {\"ngram\": \"better decisions\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3865}, {\"ngram\": \"novices\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When making critical decisions, resist the urge to call them too quickly.\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 3954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"critical decisions\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3911}, {\"ngram\": \"the urge\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take the time to gather all relevant data before declaring a winning idea.\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 4029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 3968}, {\"ngram\": \"all relevant data\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 3996}, {\"ngram\": \"a winning idea\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first-mover advantage is real, but as with Theranos' example, sometimes you need time for the unintended consequences to become evident.\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4077, \"end\": 4085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theranos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Theranos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theranos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theranos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first-mover advantage\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4055}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4119}, {\"ngram\": \"the unintended consequences\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah Lyles' Olympic victory wasn't just about speed but about winning according to precisely defined rules.\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4172, \"end\": 4182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4223}, {\"ngram\": \"precisely defined rules\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leaders can win in complex business contexts too, by intentionally taking time to process all the relevant information.\", \"from\": 4280, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leaders\", \"from\": 4280, \"to\": 4287}, {\"ngram\": \"complex business\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4315}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4354, \"to\": 4358}, {\"ngram\": \"all the relevant information\", \"from\": 4370, \"to\": 4398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing so can reduce cognitive errors and reveal the nuances others miss that could provide a competitive advantage.\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cognitive errors\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4436}, {\"ngram\": \"the nuances\", \"from\": 4448, \"to\": 4459}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4466}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitive advantage\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4514}]}]}"